everything will go back to normal.

376
00:20:48,180 --> 00:20:51,590
我会继续我原来的生活
I'll have my old life back.

377
00:20:58,860 --> 00:21:02,870
成功了 对不对？他是个混血了
It worked, didn't it? He's a hybrid.

378
00:21:02,870 --> 00:21:04,370
如果你落到Klaus手里
If Klaus gets a hold of you,

379
00:21:04,370 --> 00:21:07,640
如果他掌控着这个孩子 他就赢了
if he gets that kid, he wins.

380
00:21:07,640 --> 00:21:12,390
那就帮我把孩子藏起来
Then help me hide the baby from him.

381
00:21:12,400 --> 00:21:14,510
帮我逃走
Help me run.

382
00:21:14,510 --> 00:21:16,430
他会找到你的
He'll find you.

383
00:21:16,430 --> 00:21:17,770
他会带走你的孩子
He'll take your kid away,

384
00:21:17,770 --> 00:21:19,930
他会制造更多的混血怪物
and he'll make more hybrid monsters,

385
00:21:19,940 --> 00:21:21,770
一帮完全听命于他的奴隶
slaves who do everything he says.

386
00:21:21,770 --> 00:21:24,490
Tyler 无论你想要做什么
Tyler, whatever you're thinking of doing,

387
00:21:24,490 --> 00:21:25,940
一定还有其他办法的
there has to be another way.

388
00:21:25,940 --> 00:21:28,830
你不是这样的人
You're not like this.

389
00:21:32,280 --> 00:21:36,500
啊！这样很蠢！
Agh! That was stupid.

390
00:21:36,500 --> 00:21:38,450
离她远点
Get away from her.

391
00:21:38,450 --> 00:21:39,840
关你屁事？
What do you care?

392
00:21:39,840 --> 00:21:40,900
我说了 走开
I said, get away.

393
00:21:40,900 --> 00:21:42,290
你已经得到你想要的 滚开 
You got what you wanted. Now get lost.

394
00:21:42,290 --> 00:21:44,910
Dwayne 他要杀了我
Dwayne, he's gonna kill me.

395
00:21:44,910 --> 00:21:46,380
他还要杀了你
He's gonna kill you, too.

396
00:21:46,380 --> 00:21:47,580
他说混血儿活着
He said that hybrids

397
00:21:47,580 --> 00:21:49,100
太危险了
are too dangerous to live.

398
00:21:49,100 --> 00:21:50,100
你必须阻止他
You need to stop him.

399
00:21:50,100 --> 00:21:51,680
闭嘴！哦！
Shut up. Uh!

400
00:22:26,170 --> 00:22:27,890
