Forgive me.

401
00:22:27,890 --> 00:22:30,050
还以为你有危险
Thought you were in danger.

402
00:22:30,060 --> 00:22:33,640
看来我错了
It appears I was mistaken.

403
00:22:39,350 --> 00:22:43,230
你绝对想不到我今天有多衰
You will not believe the crap day that I'm having.

404
00:22:45,470 --> 00:22:47,990
