Let me take you home.

405
00:22:47,990 --> 00:22:49,440
Elijah…
Elijah…

406
00:22:50,810 --> 00:22:56,750
关于这个孩子你还需要多了解一些
There's something you need to know about the baby.

407
00:22:56,750 --> 00:22:58,170
Hayley.
Hayley.

408
00:22:58,170 --> 00:23:00,870
别让这一切变得更加艰难
don't make this harder than it has to be.

409
00:23:02,700 --> 00:23:05,120
放弃吧...
Give up now...

410
00:23:06,290 --> 00:23:08,680
我会很快解决的
I'll end it quick.

411
00:23:08,680 --> 00:23:10,490
说的真好
Quite an offer,

412
00:23:10,500 --> 00:23:13,600
不过我是不会这么跟你说的
though not one I'll be extending to you.

413
00:23:13,600 --> 00:23:15,550
Klaus
Klaus

414
00:23:15,550 --> 00:23:19,520
嘿 Tyler 你看上去不错
Hello, Tyler.You look well.

415
00:23:19,520 --> 00:23:23,070
不过我打算改变一下
I aim to change that.

416
00:23:28,970 --> 00:23:30,640
威胁一个怀孕的女孩
Threatening a pregnant girl

417
00:23:30,640 --> 00:23:32,840
就为了报复我
in order to exact revenge against me.

418
00:23:32,840 --> 00:23:35,640
我还从没想到过你会堕落至此
I never expected you to sink so low.

419
00:23:35,640 --> 00:23:39,650
我承认 我很有感触
I admit, I'm impressed.

420
00:23:39,650 --> 00:23:41,850
我过去常跟着你混
I used to hang out with you.

421
00:23:41,850 --> 00:23:43,570
不过我想那些事情已经一去不复返了
I guess something must have rubbed off.

422
00:23:43,570 --> 00:23:45,490
你觉得Caroline会怎么想呢
What do you think Caroline would say

423
00:23:45,490 --> 00:23:47,650
如果她看到你变成这样？
if she saw what you've become?

424
00:23:47,660 --> 00:23:50,020
也许在我告知她你死讯的时候
Perhaps I'll ask her when I call her

425
00:23:50,030 --> 00:23:52,160
会顺便问问
to tell her of your demise.

426
00:23:52,160 --> 00:23:53,990
不管我发什么了什么
Whatever happens to me,

427
00:23:54,000 --> 00:23:57,160
Caroline绝对不会停止恨你的
Caroline is never gonna stop hating you.

428
00:23:58,370 --> 00:24:02,540
来吧 伙计 再拼命点
Come on, mate. Give it a bit more effort.

429
00:24:02,540 --> 00:24:04,540
让我玩个痛快
I want to enjoy myself.

430
00:24:22,470 --> 00:24:24,550
这是什么地方？
What is this place?

431
00:24:24,550 --> 00:24:26,120
这是个花园
This is the garden.

432
00:24:26,120 --> 00:24:28,810
是我用来惩罚那些违反我规矩的吸血鬼的地方
It's where I punish vampires who break my rules,

433
00:24:28,810 --> 00:24:33,810
但很久以前 这里有别的用途
but a long time ago, used to be something else.

434
00:24:37,970 --> 00:24:41,350
说说吧 告诉我你看到了什么
Go on. Tell me what you see.

435
00:24:43,820 --> 00:24:46,520
双层结构 希腊式的圆柱
Two stories, Greek columns,

436
00:24:46,530 --> 00:24:49,160
环绕式门廊 高高的天花板
wraparound porch, high ceilings,

437
00:24:49,160 --> 00:24:51,240
还有顶窗
transom windows.

438
00:24:51,250 --> 00:24:54,530
很漂亮 那又怎样？
It's lovely. So what?

439
00:24:54,530 --> 00:24:59,370
这是我为你设计的 原本将是我们的家
So I designed it for you. It was gonna be ours.

440
00:25:03,760 --> 00:25:07,660
那…
That...

441
00:25:07,660 --> 00:25:11,130
这本应该是我们共度美好生活的地方？
this was supposed to be our happily ever after?

442
00:25:11,130 --> 00:25:13,330
你和我的
Yours and mine,

443
00:25:13,340 --> 00:25:15,500
如果你没有跟着Klaus逃走的话
except you flew the coop with Klaus.

444
00:25:15,500 --> 00:25:17,890
我已经为这个地方打好了地基
I already built the foundation for the place.

445
00:25:17,890 --> 00:25:20,170
你离开后就停工了
I halted construction after you took off.

446
00:25:20,180 --> 00:25:22,390
我打算等你回来再继续
Plan was to wait for you to return.

447
00:25:22,390 --> 00:25:23,890
但你没有
You never did.

448
00:25:23,900 --> 00:25:27,250
所以这里成了我埋藏那些背叛我的人的地方
So now it's where I bury the people who betray me.

449
00:25:27,250 --> 00:25:28,680
你那时应该跟我走的
You could've come after me.

450
00:25:28,680 --> 00:25:31,020
你和Klaus在一起 我不知道你在哪
You were with Klaus. I didn't know where.

451
00:25:31,020 --> 00:25:33,240
也不知道你还想不想和我在一起
I didn't know if you still wanted to be with me.

452
00:25:33,240 --> 00:25:34,670
你当时需要做的就是回家
All you had to do was come home.

453
00:25:34,670 --> 00:25:36,210
这比你想的要复杂得多
It was more complicated than that.

454
00:25:36,210 --> 00:25:37,370
我们离开这没多久
Not long after we left here,

455
00:25:37,380 --> 00:25:38,540
他就拿匕首扎进了我的心脏
he put a dagger in my heart

456
00:25:38,540 --> 00:25:40,380
然后把我封在棺材里九十年
and stuck me in a box for 90 years.

457
00:25:40,380 --> 00:25:42,750
他偷走我一个世纪的光阴 好像对他都不算什么
He stole a century from me like it were nothing.

458
00:25:42,750 --> 00:25:44,450
这就是他 Rebekah
That's what he does, Rebekah.

459
00:25:44,450 --> 00:25:45,970
Klaus永远都不会开心的
Klaus will never be happy.

460
00:25:45,970 --> 00:25:47,200
如果有人得到了他得不到的
He'll be damned if he ever lets anyone

461
00:25:47,200 --> 00:25:48,750
他会变得非常凶残
get something that he can't have.

462
00:25:48,750 --> 00:25:49,870
我知道
I know.

463
00:25:49,870 --> 00:25:50,990
我已经跟着他的节奏
I've been dancing to this song

464
00:25:50,990 --> 00:25:52,370
活了一千年
for 1,000 years.

465
00:25:52,370 --> 00:25:55,560
从现在开始 你还有一个选择
Starting right now, you have a choice

466
00:25:55,560 --> 00:25:57,510
在一个随心所欲 任意剥夺你的快乐
between the brother who takes away your happiness

467
00:25:57,510 --> 00:25:59,810
的哥哥和一个想给你
whenever he feels like it and the man who wants

468
00:25:59,820 --> 00:26:02,270
全世界的男人之间做出选择
to give you everything you ever wanted.

469
00:26:06,820 --> 00:26:10,220
他会当着我的面杀了你
He will kill you in front of my eyes

470
00:26:10,230 --> 00:26:12,240
为了泄恨
out of spite.

471
00:26:12,240 --> 00:26:15,610
如果我们先摆脱他就不一定了
Not if we get rid of him first.

472
00:26:18,830 --> 00:26:21,080
Klaus肯定已经知道了
Klaus must have known.

473
00:26:21,090 --> 00:26:24,040
这是唯一的解释
That's the only explanation.

474
00:26:24,040 --> 00:26:25,540
他一点也不在乎这个孩子
He could care less about the baby.

475
00:26:25,540 --> 00:26:26,910
他只是想让孩子生下来
He just wants her to be born

476
00:26:26,910 --> 00:26:29,630
这样他就能制造更多的混血儿
so he can use her to make more sired hybrids.

477
00:26:32,010 --> 00:26:35,920
尽管Dwayne表现出来的
Although the way that Dwayne was acting,

478
00:26:35,920 --> 00:26:39,470
更像是对我认祖归宗了
it was more like he was sired to me.

479
00:26:41,190 --> 00:26:44,760
我应该带你回家
I should take you home.

480
00:26:44,760 --> 00:26:48,030
开什么玩笑？哪里是家？
Are you serious? Home to what?

481
00:26:48,030 --> 00:26:49,810
听着 不管我弟弟的意图如何
Look. Regardless of my brother's intentions,

482
00:26:49,820 --> 00:26:51,600
我始终如一
mine remain the same.

483
00:26:51,600 --> 00:26:53,870
我说过会保护你
I said that I would protect you,

484
00:26:53,870 --> 00:26:56,490
就算是Klaus想伤害你也不行
even, if need be, from Klaus himself.

485
00:26:56,490 --> 00:26:59,270
我可以自己照顾自己
I can take care of myself.

486
00:26:59,270 --> 00:27:01,290
我一直都是靠自己的
I've done it for a long time.

487
00:27:04,280 --> 00:27:06,960
这就是你的复仇计划吗 Tyler？
Is this your idea of revenge, Tyler,

488
00:27:06,970 --> 00:27:08,750
累人的捉迷藏游戏？
grueling game of hide-and-seek?


















