呀！呀！
Raagh! Raagh!

491
00:27:39,320 --> 00:27:40,820
你狗胆包天？
How dare you?

492
00:27:40,820 --> 00:27:42,740
这才刚刚开始
I'm just getting started.

493
00:27:42,740 --> 00:27:45,320
啊！
Aagh!

494
00:27:45,330 --> 00:27:47,080
你已经开始饥渴了
You've grown bloodthirsty.

495
00:27:47,080 --> 00:27:48,990
