看到你这个样子
to see you like this.

497
00:27:50,450 --> 00:27:53,080
哈哈哈！
Ha ha ha!

498
00:28:00,260 --> 00:28:03,410
真是可悲
It's sad, really.

499
00:28:03,410 --> 00:28:05,790
我本以为我把你变得更好
I thought I made you better.

500
00:28:05,800 --> 00:28:08,630
没想到你却让人失望
Turns out, you're quite the disappointment.

501
00:28:08,630 --> 00:28:10,930
呀！
Yaah!

502
00:28:10,940 --> 00:28:13,100
我猜我只不过是你另一个失败品而已
I guess I'm another one of your failures,

503
00:28:13,100 --> 00:28:15,850
就像你制造混血最终失败一样
like how you failed at making hybrids,

504
00:28:15,860 --> 00:28:17,890
