how you failed your family.

505
00:28:20,610 --> 00:28:21,780
现在看起来你甚至可能
Now it looks like you're even

506
00:28:21,780 --> 00:28:24,810
要让你自己的孩子失望了
gonna fail your own kid.

507
00:28:24,820 --> 00:28:28,650
那就这样终结你乏味又渺小的一生吧
And thus ends your tedious, little life.

508
00:28:28,650 --> 00:28:30,450
至少它不会耗时太久
At least it was brief.

509
00:28:30,450 --> 00:28:32,700
呀！啊！！
Yaagh! Ugh...

510
00:28:35,160 --> 00:28:37,280
杀了我吧
Do it.

511
00:28:37,280 --> 00:28:40,050
你永远不会毁掉我的
You're never gonna break me.

512
00:28:40,050 --> 00:28:41,660
你唯一能做的就是杀了我
Only thing you could do is kill me.

513
00:28:41,670 --> 00:28:46,130
来吧  杀了我  让一切都结束
So go on. Go on. Get it over with.

514
00:28:46,140 --> 00:28:48,670
啊…
Ah...

515
00:28:48,670 --> 00:28:53,310
你想让我结束你的痛苦  是吗？
You want me to end your suffering, don't you?

516
00:28:53,310 --> 00:28:58,230
嗯？我确实毁掉了你  夺走了你的一切
Hmm? I did break you, took everything from you,

517
00:28:58,230 --> 00:29:00,970
