520
00:29:16,420 --> 00:29:18,500
更好的方式是让你生不如死
It's better to let you live,

521
00:29:18,500 --> 00:29:20,650
每个清晨你醒来就会意识到
and each morning, you will wake knowing

522
00:29:20,650 --> 00:29:23,510
你这样卑微的活着
that your wretched existence continues

523
00:29:23,510 --> 00:29:27,090
仅仅是由于我的施舍
only by my will.

524
00:29:27,090 --> 00:29:31,350
现在你走吧  去享受你剩下的日子吧
Now go and live the rest of your days

525
00:29:31,350 --> 00:29:36,550
你要知道你对我来说什么都不是
knowing you are nothing to me.

526
00:29:43,560 --> 00:29:45,090
你知道曾经有多少傻子试图要
Do you know how many fools have tried

527
00:29:45,100 --> 00:29:46,700
战胜我哥哥么?
to vanquish my brother?

528
00:29:46,700 --> 00:29:48,780
如果你和他对立  他会杀了你
If you stand against him, he will kill you,

529
00:29:48,780 --> 00:29:50,730
那种可怕又血腥的场面
and it will be awful and bloody,

530
00:29:50,730 --> 00:29:53,020
我绝对不会旁观的
and I will not stand around and watch.

531
00:29:53,020 --> 00:29:56,960
你忘了我有一个秘密武器…Davina
You forget I have a secret weapon... Davina,

532
00:29:56,960 --> 00:29:59,410
