the most powerful witch in the last couple centuries.

533
00:29:59,410 --> 00:30:02,740
如果她能找出杀掉你哥哥的办法呢？
What if she can find a way to kill him?

534
00:30:04,530 --> 00:30:07,300
你什么都不知道 是吗？
You don't know, do you?

535
00:30:07,300 --> 00:30:08,950
你杀了Klaus的话
You can't kill Klaus,

536
00:30:08,950 --> 00:30:11,420
自己也会跟着死
not without dying yourself.

537
00:30:11,420 --> 00:30:12,590
从我哥哥Kol和Finn的死亡中
We learned it from the deaths

538
00:30:12,590 --> 00:30:13,720
我们知道了一些事情
of my brothers Kol and Finn.

539
00:30:13,720 --> 00:30:15,440
如果一个始祖吸血鬼死了  
If an Original dies, every vampire

540
00:30:15,440 --> 00:30:18,630
那他们这条血脉的吸血鬼都会跟着死去
ever made from their line dies with him.

541
00:30:18,630 --> 00:30:21,550
即使你杀死了Klaus 他也终将是赢家
Even if you kill Klaus, he'll still win.

542
00:30:21,550 --> 00:30:23,430
一千年来都是这样
It's been that way for 1,000 years.

543
00:30:23,430 --> 00:30:25,270
那就是他的诀窍  他永远都是赢家
That's his trick. He always wins.

544
00:30:25,270 --> 00:30:27,190
还有一个方法
There's another way.

545
00:30:27,190 --> 00:30:29,190
什么方法？
What would that be?

546
00:30:29,190 --> 00:30:31,360
我们把他永远的埋在这里
